name: Spaceport Docking Bay
LocationDStext: Your docking bay transit from here requires 3 Force. Your pilots deploy +1 here. May not be deployed to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth or Yavin 4.
LocationLStext: Your docking bay transit from here requires 2 Force. Your starfighters deploy -1 (or 2 is freighter) here. May not be deployed to Bespin, Dagobah, Endor, Hoth or Yavin 4.
